Test SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH support. Output a document with the environment variable SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH set to 2000-01-01 00:00 UTC and check that the document contains the timestamp that corresponds to this date (given as an argument).

Parameters ---------- fmt : {"pdf", "ps", "svg"} Output format. string : bytes Timestamp string for 2000-01-01 00:00 UTC.
